@startuml Redux_Cart_Overview
title Redux Cart - High Level Overview

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam BoxPadding 10

rectangle "React Component\n(user action)" as UI
rectangle "cartAction\n(create action object)" as Action
rectangle "cartStore\n(dispatch)" as Store
rectangle "cartReducer\n(update cart state)" as Reducer
rectangle "Subscribed UI\n(re-render)" as View
database "localStorage\n(cart persistence)" as Storage

UI --> Action : add / remove / update quantity
Action --> Store : action
Store --> Reducer : current state + action
Reducer --> Store : new state
Store --> View : state changed
Store --> Storage : persist cart items

@enduml